<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE paragraph PUBLIC "-//IFRS//DTD DITA Paragraph//EN" "../../../DocTypes/com.ifrs.doctype/dtd/paragraph.dtd"><paragraph id="IAS08_31" base="SL29868" principles="no"><paranum class="- topic/title paragraph/paranum "/><titlealts><navtitle>31</navtitle></titlealts><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS 8"/><data name="paranum" value="31"/></prolog><body><p id="IAS08_P0111">In complying with <xref id="IAS08_X0158" base="A8-113" href="IAS08_30.dita#IAS08_30">paragraph 30</xref>, an entity considers disclosing: </p><ol outputclass="static" id="IAS08_L0018" base="SL141526" type="lower-alpha"><li id="IAS08_31_a"><li_value>(a)</li_value>         <p id="IAS08_P0112" base="SL141528">the title of the new IFRS;</p>       </li><li id="IAS08_31_b"><li_value>(b)</li_value>         <p id="IAS08_P0113" base="SL141530">the nature of the impending change or changes in accounting policy;</p>       </li><li id="IAS08_31_c"><li_value>(c)</li_value>         <p id="IAS08_P0114" base="SL141532">the date by which application of the IFRS is required;</p>       </li><li id="IAS08_31_d"><li_value>(d)</li_value>         <p id="IAS08_P0115" base="SL141534">the date as at which it plans to apply the IFRS initially; and</p>       </li><li id="IAS08_31_e"><li_value>(e)</li_value>         <p id="IAS08_P0116" base="SL141536">either:</p>         <ol outputclass="static" id="IAS08_L0019" base="SL141537" type="lower-roman"><li id="IAS08_31_e_i"><li_value>(i)</li_value>             <p id="IAS08_P0117" base="SL141539">a discussion of the impact that initial application of the IFRS is expected to have on the entity’s financial statements; or</p>           </li><li id="IAS08_31_e_ii"><li_value>(ii)</li_value>             <p id="IAS08_P0118" base="SL141541">if that impact is not known or reasonably estimable, a statement to that effect.</p>           </li></ol>       </li></ol></body></paragraph>